rComments: It was his first time teaching at UFV and for sure he is everybody's favorite now learned so much from him. Take him if you want to learn and enjoy the course at the same time. He makes programming so interesting with his happy go nature. Would love to take him again.
Uses lots of analogies to help understanding.
Great prof, really funny and conveys the material effectively.

Going to class is a must in order to learn the material well. Opeyami is a great speaker once you get used to his accent. He asks questions that are related to the material and his quizs are simple but will give you better understanding. Don't be afraid to ask questions during class.
Funniest Prof, he tries to teach the material the best he can and codes on screen sometimes to improve teaching. He is so friendly and nice and his jokes will crack you up. Total recommend.
